Sleep Tracker Application

Stack:
- Angular (primary)
- Bootstrap (grid layout and icons only)
- Node.js express (backend)

API:
- OpenAI api


IMPORTANT NOTE: 
- I removed token key - was unsure if I should submit it or not 

setup: 
Setting up API Key: 
cd ./server/.env
and create a .env file
format:
API: 
Key: 300


Project Set up: 
- Create server/.env file and place API="KEY" and PORT=3000
- cd client folder, run npm install
- cd server folder, run npm install

Starting Project:
- cd server
- run npm run dev
- open a second powershell and cd to client
- run npm start
- Go to: http://localhost:4200